<span class="openapi-clients-box"></span><span id="/reference/store/store-actors-collection/get-list-of-actors-in-store"></span><span id="/reference/store/get-list-of-actors-in-store"></span>Gets the list of public Actors in Apify Store. You can use `search`
parameter to search Actors by string in title, name, description, username
and readme.

If you need detailed info about a specific Actor, use the [Get
actor](#/reference/actors/actor-object/get-actor) endpoint.


The endpoint supports pagination using the `limit` and `offset` parameters.
It will not return more than 1,000 records.
